HEADWORD: Redif
<hw>Re*dif"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Turk.
<ets>red⟦imac⟧f</ets>, fr. <ets>rad⟦imac⟧f</ets>, orig., he who rides
behind another on the same beast, fr. <ets>radaf</ets> to follow.]</ety>
<def>A reserve force in the Turkish army, or a soldier of the reserve.
